{[#]How should White meet Black's obvious intention to simplify with ...a7-a5 
(with or without the previous ...Nc6)?} 28. Rbc1 $1 $16 {This is the only way
to parry both threats mechanically.} (28. Rxd4 $6 a5 29. Rc4 Na6 $11) (28. Ra1
$6 Nc6 $14) 28... Na6 {Black might have relied on a move repetition due to the
weakness on b4, but White can do better.} 29. Rxd4 Nxb4 30. Rc8+ Kh7 31. Rc7 {
