seventh rank is hopelessly weak.} Rb7 $2 {Just a blunder.} (31... f6 32. Rdd7
$18) (31... Kg6 32. Rg4+ Kf6 33. Rf4+) (31... Kg8 32. Rd8+ Kh7 33. Rxf7 $18)
32. Rxb7 {Winning the knight, 1-0 Andersson, U (2605)-Agdestein, S (2560) Wijk
aan Zee 1988} *

